name: Computer Science Organization
body:
### About
TAMS Computer Science Organization is a club dedicated to improving ability in computer science. We focus on everything related to computer science, including algorithms, web design, game programming, and more.

[Join us on Facebook for updates!](http://www.facebook.com/groups/tamscompsci/)

### GAs
Our club meets bi-weekly on Mondays and Thursdays in the conference room. Mondays at 8 PM are reserved for algorithms, and Thursdays at 9 PM are for the GA and beginner lessons.

### Club Execs
* [Ian Macalinao](http://ianmacalinao.com) ([@simplyianm](http://github.com/simplyianm)) - President
* [Tyler O'Meara](http://tyleromeara.com) ([@Acidity](http://github.com/Acidity)) - Vice President
* [Sherwin Thomas](#) - Club Coordinator
* [Krzysztof Drewniak](#) ([@krzysz00](http://github.com/krzysz00)) - Coach
